   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Professional Development Education (PDE) &#x2013; 2020 - research management and governance - Research Capacity Building Workshop Series</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program aims to provide dialogue, insights and learning to research and science sector in Indonesia and further promote UK excellence in science and innovation through building sustainable partnership between UK and Indonesia. The workshops will be designed for researchers and research managers.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The workshop series will help increasing capacity of research sector in Indonesia. Topics could include: Research Management; International Publication; Managing IPRs and patent register</narrative>
